        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3034199781" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8968617919686991505">Don&apos;t know if this counts as a spoiler, but when I reached the part about the Mother Superior receiving an enema as part of her exorcism and having it held in public view as a spectator event, well Aldous may have topped his LSD reporting in terms of literary outrage. </span>
  <span id="freeText8968617919686991505" style="display:none">Don't know if this counts as a spoiler, but when I reached the part about the Mother Superior receiving an enema as part of her exorcism and having it held in public view as a spectator event, well Aldous may have topped his LSD reporting in terms of literary outrage. </span>
